Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. David Hawkins. I've been a psychiatrist for the last 35 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've worked in the field of psychoanalysis, all kinds of psychotherapy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,done research on the relationship between nutrition and brain chemistry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and its relationship to emotions and emotional and mental disorders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the last 10 years, I've been doing research on the nature of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and its extensions into that field of knowledge man calls spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In our talk today, we'll be talking about how to meet the major crises of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Death, divorce, separation, disfigurement, injury, accident, catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Those serious things which result in emotional overwhelms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What techniques can we utilize to handle these experiences?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.56,0:01:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And in doing that, we'll be referring, as we have in these other talks,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to a map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A map of consciousness, which gives us a point of reference
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and allows us a greater understanding of what we'll be talking about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this map, you'll see it's a mathematical model.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the box, this represents the human ego, the self with a small self,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,are various levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're named according to common human experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Guilt and apathy and grief and fear, desire, anger, pride, courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,willingness, acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Love, joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As we get towards the top, we reach, we get closer and closer to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we get to the bottom, we get farther and farther from the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll notice that death is calibrated at zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And so these numbers indicate the relative energies, the power of these energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So that apathy is, for instance, half as powerful as fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear has half the energy of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And neutral has half the energy of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we can get a feeling for the relative power of these different positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're really coming out of points of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice that there are arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So that everything below courage, you'll notice all the arrows go to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Indicating that the effect is destructive, that the effect is anti-life,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,does not support life, and is in violation of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we pass above the level of truth, which is courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll notice that the needle swings to the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we get beyond that, into areas of lovingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll notice that the arrows go to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Indicating that these energy fields nurture and support life, and are aligned with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:03:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In the subject for today, acute catastrophic experiences, which are overwhelming,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be referring to these energy fields then,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,for a greater understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we'll be talking about techniques with which to handle these emotional overwhelms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In these experiences, life suddenly becomes a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's suddenly overwhelmed by an emotional storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How to handle this acute event.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How to shorten the period, and how to relieve the pain and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Diminish it to the minimum, will be the techniques we're talking about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these major life experiences,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,have something in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They all represent, to the mind, a major loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,An acute catastrophic loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They all indicate a major change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And they all have in common, the feeling of powerlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of their permanency, the mind gets that it cannot do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That it is stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is this phenomenon of being stopped, the permanence, the fact that one is powerless,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and cannot change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And cannot change the event, that is partially responsible, for the acute upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And how to handle this, will depend on our orientation to the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And our knowledge of the whole field of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these experiences, unleash a storm of negative feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shock, disbelief, denial, anger, guilt, attempts at undoing, self-blame, resentment, feelings of abandonment,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,rage at God and oneself, self-pity, rage at the world, rage at the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All these negative emotions surface and come on at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes in sequence, sometimes in combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But in general, there is a massive overwhelm of negative emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That they all share in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The acute separation, the acute sense of loss, the acute sense of overwhelm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And the sequencing of first the shock, then the resentment,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the disbelief, the anger. The sequencing of these varies from experience to experience and person
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to person. Their exact sequence is immaterial. What is significant is that they are unleashing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of everything at the bottom of the box. We said that everything in the bottom of the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field, is in a negative direction. And when one of these energy fields becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,strong, it tends to pull the rest with it. So that grief over loss then seems to bring with it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,guilt, senses of hopelessness, fear of the future, desire to change the whole thing, anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole negative energy field is unleashed in one giant emergency, and the emergency really is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,one of energy. The problem is really being that of being overwhelmed by a massive unleashing of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind tries to use reason. It tries to think its way out of this dilemma. It tries to find
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,explanations and reasons. It can't succeed in this because the energy field overwhelm is so massive
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that the thoughts become merely a reflection of the negativity of the energy field. And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the thoughts themselves become negative. So now one is beset by an overwhelm of energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,an overwhelm of negative energy. And then one is beset by the overwhelming of negative energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So one is beset by an overwhelm of negative energy. And now one is beset by an overwhelm of negative energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of negative emotion and an overwhelm of negative thoughts. How to meet this crisis is our talk for
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,today. Another thing that all these experiences share in common is that they are all at the top
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of life stress rating scales. You know there are scales that rate numerically from zero to a hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The degree of stress of certain life events and the ones that we're talking about today are all
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,at the top of the list. Death of a spouse, death of a child, death of a family member, divorce, all of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,these rate 100 on the rating scale. The other ones we mentioned rate maybe 95 to 96, 97. So the ones
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,we're talking about today are the maximal catastrophes which we can face in our whole
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences of life. How to convert these into acute gains, how to maximize them, how to use them
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as a springboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For a major leap in consciousness. We need to look then at consciousness itself and as we have in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,other talks we'll be talking about the relationship between body, mind and spirit. What is that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,relationship? What is its exact nature and how can it be helpful to us in our understanding of today's
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,topic? And so we'll review again as we have in the other talks the fact that the body is unable to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:08:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,experience itself. The body has no capacity to experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is. It is actually insentient. How do we know where the body is? Well, because of sensations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't experience the body. We experience sensations of the body. Sensations themselves have no way of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,being experienced. They're experienced in something greater than themselves and that is in mind itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Our awareness of what is going on in body then is because it's being reported and experienced within mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, mind itself has no capacity within itself to experience itself. That seems like a shocking thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But a memory cannot experience its own memoryness. A thought cannot experience its own thoughtness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Feelings cannot experience their own feelingness. It's because they are experienced in something greater than mind
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:09:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is consciousness itself. It is because of consciousness that you're aware of what is going on in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind then reports what is going on with sensations. Sensations report what is going on with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And so where we are experiencing then is several levels removed from the body itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness itself is unable to actually experience itself. It is because of an absolute energy field beyond that called knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is absolute that we are aware then and know what is going on within consciousness which is reporting
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,what is going on in mind, which is reporting what is going on in sensations, which is reporting what goes on with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore where we experience, that which we really are, is considerably removed from the physical body itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because experiencing is going on within consciousness that we can address the solution to human problems
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,directly within the field of consciousness itself, thereby effectively shortening and relieving the amount
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of pain and suffering and bringing about a far more effective result.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw the result of this technique and this approach in our talks on the handling of physical pain and sickness and suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of depression, anxiety and fear. And the same technique will work in meeting these acute emotional catastrophic emergencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you actually live is in the experience of your own experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A person thinks, well, I live in the world, I'm experiencing the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is coming in and it's being registered in your experience of your experience of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We can handle anything if we address then this exact focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If we focus on where we're experiencing experience, we can handle things with precision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:11:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can in moments and minutes handle things that would take weeks, months, years and in fact lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can handle within an hour a thing that others have been unable to handle in an entire lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We know people who have had these catastrophic events early in life and we see them in older age and it's still not over with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The resentment, the bitterness, the anger, the disillusionment, the rage, the major decisions that come out of those negative feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,are still with the person 50 years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though the event happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still unhealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There hasn't been the knowledge present of how to handle this overwhelm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And so today we're talking about directly how to handle the overwhelm at the level at which it is being experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To look at the experiencing, the field of the experiencing and to be aware where experiencing is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Experiencing is not happening out in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Experience is not happening in your foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not happening in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not happening in your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening within consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you examine where you experience experience, you'll find that it's everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't experience things in a focal point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a belief system of the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, if I say to someone who hasn't looked into this, where do you experience your thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of habit, the person points to their head and says here, that's a belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your thought about thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You think your thoughts here, but that's only a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think that thought, that your thoughts are thought here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As you really go into it and introspect a little bit with a little contemplation and reflection,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see that experiencing is diffuse, that it's going on everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had to put your finger on where is experiencing happening, you cannot put your finger on any particular place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like everywhere and nowhere simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is that particular point which we'll be working with today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In doing this, we'll say something surprising, but something that makes this kind of work precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know because I've worked with it clinically for over 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know because I've been through most of the major life crises myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, in the last few years, I've been through half a dozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I will share my own experience of the truth of these things
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,because all of them can be experienced within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that you have to handle in these acute catastrophic events is the emotions themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of the emotion is the only thing you have to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact that if we look at the experience, we'll see it's not the event that happened in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:14:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,or that we think has happened in the world that is our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the way we feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about facts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Facts don't mean anything in and of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your emotional reaction to the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A fact is only a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how we feel about that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And so therefore, the only thing we really ever have to handle about the events in life is our feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Our feelings come from our attitudes, our beliefs, our way of being with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the way we view ourself and the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So that will give a variety to the emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But in an overwhelm, our problem is going to be handling just the emotional energy itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even really have to handle the emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to handle is the energy of the emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you say, but what about the events out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do now with no money?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do with no husband, etc., etc.?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, the events are very easy to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no acute catastrophe that the events themselves are merely just handled in a mechanical way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the feelings are aside, you may have reluctance, you may have some resentment, you may have regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But these are minor things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The handling of the actual issues within the phenomenal world, within your daily life, are going to be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not the real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought that they are a real problem is just coming out of the negative emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that they seem catastrophic and hopeless and unbearable and insurmountable is merely coming out of the energy field of the emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you come out on the other side of it, life adjusts itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Life adjusts itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Something else comes in to fill the vacuum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Life goes right on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I go right on doing carpentry work even though I lost the thumb that was essential to doing it all of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is really not how am I going to learn to do carpentry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is really not where am I going to start another business again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I going to start earning money again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are simple once the emotions are out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Life presents the solutions to all problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Necessity is the mother of invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So whatever the dilemma is that appears in one's life, it will resolve itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You will meet somebody new.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of life resumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Life goes right on no matter how major the catastrophe seems at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So our problem is not handling the event out there, not handling the circumstances of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They will handle themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, usually relatives will handle it for you while you are knocked out of the box by the overwhelm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem then is handling the energies which are arising.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We said once one of these major negative energy fields releases itself, starts to unleash itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that it tends to drag the rest with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarely do you experience grief alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There is also almost always guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Grief is associated with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Blaming yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I look, you know, as I went around the turn, why didn't I put chains on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I take her to the doctor sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could have cured her cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I bet on that horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of a retrospective self-recrimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There is also apathy, hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Life seems hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we will never be happy again, like the source of happiness has left our life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the grief is natural to the loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there are the fears that arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How will I live without whatever it is that I have lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The constant, incessant desire drives us crazy to try and change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The bargaining, the trying to manipulate, the arguing with God, the making bargains with God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh God, if you only let so and so live, I will do this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the anger, the rage at life, at the nature of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger displaced onto the people of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the doctor's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sue the doctor if the patient died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The anger at the spouse for having disrupted the marriage and lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these negative energies usually unleash all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And from moment to moment, one or the other may be dominant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As we said before, at the same time, the mind is thrashing around wildly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to come up with explanations, trying to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We are swamped by the overflow of the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Overflow of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is that the energy is too much for the apparatus to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes into disorganization, into biologic overwhelm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And the acute stress throws the person into acute emergency emotions and an acute emergency state,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,especially to work in consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The problems are not best handled on the level at which they seem to be occurring,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but on the next higher energy level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher energy means greater power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Handle there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It handles it automatically on the lower levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to handle then are the energies of the emotional overwhelm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that sound surprising for a psychiatrist to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people would expect that a psychiatrist would begin talking about the psychology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The psychology, the intricate relationship between the person and these events and what they mean symbolically.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The psychological components.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're going to bypass all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to talk about the fact that the emotions that are released, whatever the psychology,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening is a massive release of these negative emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is it about the emotions that we're interested in is the energy of the emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the technique which we found very, very effective is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We ignore the thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the mind is never going to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind does not have the capacity to figure it out and handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It is in a massive overwhelm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The issues are extraordinarily complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And to unravel it would take a lifetime if you really wanted to know the full significance
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and every contribution from every level of one's psychological self to the total meaning of these experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't really have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a very good thing that we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have to go into the feeling itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Notice that the feeling is being felt in a general way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We notice that the feeling has below it an energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though consciousness works this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though there's a diffuse body of energy which really has no name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We could call it the energy of emotionalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy behind feelingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Given a moment of time, this diffuse, unnamed energy will begin to take form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It will begin to take the form, let's say, of grief or anger or rage or indignation, self-pity, whatever, jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This emotional feel which now has some kind of form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,At first it's diffuse and formless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But it now begins to take something of the form of grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's also some fear in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also some anger in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of diffuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of, we might call it, the energy of negative emotions in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow it a split second longer and it will now take a greater form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.81,0:21:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say a specific fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, how will I live now without money or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear begins to take form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then out of the specific emotion, let us say in this case fear, thoughts begin to arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like a sequence of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like an ocean of suppressed energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And what we'll be doing today is talking about how to decompress it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How to decompress it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can cut the fuse, if we can pull the plug, then we've disconnected the whole experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're left then with an inner state of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So what I'd like you to do today is to accept, to take my word for the fact that you don't have to do anything about the external events.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't make any progress by looking at the thoughts because they are endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not really going to get much headway in handling it by looking at the specific emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But you will get a very profound effect if you allow yourself to focus on the energy below the upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As you catch the experience earlier and earlier, you will get that this energy is diffuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost nameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:23:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a container of...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...pressurized gas that's seeking release.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And this pressurized emotion, the energy of it, has been accumulating for a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.84,0:23:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the suppressed emotion that has accumulated up to this point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And it now has an out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.84,0:23:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So the event that has happened in life has opened the sluices, has opened the gates, has opened the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And all this container of compressed, suppressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...emotional energy is now using this opportunity to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the barn door is open, all the animals run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.84,0:23:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How to get out of the way of these running animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,One way to cut through it quickly is to accept the fact that you can't escape this experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to escape it only prolongs it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.22,0:23:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem the mind will try to figure out ways to escape it as though that will reduce the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.22,0:24:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, the pain comes from resisting the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.22,0:24:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain comes from resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.22,0:24:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we'll use somewhat the same technique we did with physical pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.22,0:24:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where we surrender, we let go resisting this energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.22,0:24:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We just sit down and let go resisting it and choose to be with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.22,0:24:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The faster we open it up, the faster we let that energy out, the quicker the experience will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.22,0:24:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of dragging it out endlessly, agonizingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.22,0:24:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...over the hours and the weeks and the days.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.22,0:24:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And the months and the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.22,0:24:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the whole lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.22,0:24:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole thing can be let go of.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.22,0:24:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember we said when somebody had an acute injury to their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.22,0:24:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say a burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.22,0:24:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If the person stops everything and does this very same practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.22,0:24:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.22,0:24:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just opens the door and welcomes in and says, in fact, I want more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.22,0:24:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the energy of that experience and ignores what goes on in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.22,0:24:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignores thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.22,0:24:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But allows themselves merely to experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.22,0:25:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To experience this energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.01,0:25:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mind will say, well I'm experiencing grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.15,0:25:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a label.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.27,0:25:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll say all thoughts are labels and they have no reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.38,0:25:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality, none of these things exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.38,0:25:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all labels we've put on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.38,0:25:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To say that it is grief and the mind expects if a loved one dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.38,0:25:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Automatically it says, grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.44,0:25:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Grief is a label.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.02,0:25:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind having the power that it does over emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.02,0:25:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind having the capacity to give it form.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.02,0:25:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The belief that to lose someone is automatically therefore grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.01,0:25:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gives form to the emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.01,0:25:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of the emotions is actually form less.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.18,0:25:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But we insist that it's grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.18,0:25:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It then takes the form of grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.18,0:25:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If somebody holds a gun to our head.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.56,0:25:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're convinced naturally in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.56,0:25:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That this calls for fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.56,0:25:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore the same energy now assumes a somewhat different form.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.56,0:26:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Labeled fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.18,0:26:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to decrease the form of the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.18,0:26:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And stop labeling it anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.18,0:26:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't tell people, you know, I'm going through grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.36,0:26:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going through fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.36,0:26:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going through an upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.52,0:26:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Upset is closer to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.52,0:26:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Upset is a general term.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.52,0:26:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's very hard to say what the emotion is in an acute upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.52,0:26:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Initially what is experienced usually is a sense of shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.52,0:26:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A sense of numbness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.52,0:26:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A sense of disbelief.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.52,0:26:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't believe that this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.81,0:26:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the moment to begin this practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.81,0:26:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To know about it in advance, you're prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.81,0:26:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing about it in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.91,0:26:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I recently, only a few months ago, went through such an experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.00,0:26:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And instantly began letting go, resisting the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.00,0:26:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Constantly canceling out the thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.00,0:26:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Canceling out the thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.00,0:26:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The loss, for instance, seems forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.00,0:26:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.00,0:26:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.17,0:26:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't the loss of a lifetime that is the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.17,0:27:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the energy of the emotion that's coming up about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.20,0:27:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the energy of the emotion about that dissipates,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.20,0:27:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that, let's say, you're never going to grow another thumb again,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.20,0:27:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is sort of a so what.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.20,0:27:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've learned to do things with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.32,0:27:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuffle cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.32,0:27:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Count money.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.32,0:27:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the pages of the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.77,0:27:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That would seem like an impossible loss becomes sort of a so what.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.77,0:27:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is that acute catastrophic emotionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.16,0:27:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all we have to do is be with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.16,0:27:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The technique is to allow yourself to experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.16,0:27:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, to get it over with in a hurry, just ask for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.16,0:27:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Say to yourself, I want more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.16,0:27:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.16,0:27:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see as we talk later in our discussion about the energy fields here,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.34,0:27:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is a major opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.48,0:27:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The cause of all pain and suffering is the accumulation of this compressed energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.48,0:27:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And life events allow us an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.48,0:28:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It opens the gate so that we allow ourselves to feel some of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.48,0:28:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We put some of this on a...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.48,0:28:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say somebody bumps the fender of your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.48,0:28:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All the suppressed anger that you've accumulated over your lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.48,0:28:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,now has an excuse to pop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.48,0:28:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets angry over the dented fender.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.48,0:28:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets annoyed over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.48,0:28:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes into self-pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.48,0:28:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes into jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.48,0:28:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The events in life are the excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.47,0:28:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuses, and what were their excuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.47,0:28:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the compressed energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.78,0:28:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the compressed energy becomes unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.78,0:28:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind then finds a way for it to discharge that is acceptable to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.85,0:28:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A person who is familiar with this will feel the compressed energy
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.85,0:28:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to release it without waiting for the mind to create an excuse
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.85,0:28:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that justifies the release of this energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.85,0:28:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The more sophisticated mind doesn't need an event out there to release its angriness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.85,0:28:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It just knows that it's building up some suppressed angriness,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.85,0:29:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and it sits down and it says,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.85,0:29:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I better look at this,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.85,0:29:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and starts letting go the energy of it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.85,0:29:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,before the mind gets around and has to create something out there
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.85,0:29:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to relieve itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.85,0:29:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though the events in our life are almost like safety valves,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.85,0:29:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,release valves,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.85,0:29:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,a way to decompress this energy tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.85,0:29:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And so our technique today is one of decompression.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.85,0:29:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's looking at the energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.85,0:29:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at it where it's being experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.85,0:29:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to handle the thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.85,0:29:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to handle the problems that the mind creates now
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.85,0:29:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,around this particular event.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.01,0:29:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When you look at any life experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.01,0:29:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see you only live within your feelings about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.01,0:29:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The life event itself is really a nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.10,0:29:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In the morning, it may look catastrophic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.10,0:29:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,By noon, it might be amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.10,0:29:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The event hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.10,0:29:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The dented fender at the moment that it happens may be an outrage,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.10,0:29:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're in indignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.10,0:29:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And then as you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.10,0:30:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you start to feel guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.10,0:30:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know very well you turned a little too sharply yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.21,0:30:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe an hour later, you're feeling sorry for the other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.21,0:30:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He now has an insurance problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.21,0:30:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize it really wasn't his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.21,0:30:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you have a desire to make it up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.21,0:30:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're feeling guilty and blaming yourself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.21,0:30:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you think about it again, and now you go back into rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.21,0:30:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what you're living with.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.21,0:30:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you living with the dented fender?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.21,0:30:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact is you never really live with the dented fender.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.21,0:30:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You only live with your own inner experience of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.21,0:30:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how you are with that that you are experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.21,0:30:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We never experience the dented fenders in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.21,0:30:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We only experience our emotions about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.21,0:30:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that simplifies it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.36,0:30:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes it simple, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.36,0:30:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not quite as bad and overwhelmed now when you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.36,0:30:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing you're ever going to have to handle is an energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.36,0:30:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that subtle inner feelingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.36,0:30:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,letting go, resisting it, surrendering to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.36,0:30:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,welcoming it, saying yes to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.36,0:31:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,releases the energy of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.36,0:31:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After you do this for a few minutes or maybe an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.65,0:31:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on how adept, some people get it right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.65,0:31:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,other people it takes a little practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.65,0:31:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But as you sort of get where it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.65,0:31:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you no longer have to even experience the emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.65,0:31:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to handle or experience any of these emotions as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.65,0:31:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That which was fear disappears and is not felt as fear anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.65,0:31:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger is not felt as anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.05,0:31:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Guiltiness is not felt as guilt per se.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.05,0:31:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It is felt as an overwhelming upcoming flow of a negative energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.05,0:31:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,which actually is nameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.05,0:31:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When you stop naming it anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.05,0:31:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,when you stop labeling it,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.05,0:31:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,when you stop calling it anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.05,0:31:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,when you stop putting constructions of the mind onto it,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.05,0:31:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,when you stop putting interpretations onto it,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.05,0:32:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,when you let go of right and wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.05,0:32:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,let go wanting to make it wrong, the event wrong, yourself wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.05,0:32:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,when you bypass all that and go directly to the energy of the feelingness of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.05,0:32:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see you don't have to handle all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.05,0:32:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to handle the thoughts about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.05,0:32:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even have to handle the emotions of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.19,0:32:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is handle this upcoming energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.19,0:32:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do that? Yes, you can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.19,0:32:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're doing it all the time anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.22,0:32:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The ineffective technique of wildly racing around in your mind trying to figure it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.22,0:32:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,wildly running around inside your mind trying to handle these catastrophic emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.22,0:32:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,at the same time this letting go of the energy field is happening anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.60,0:32:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So today all we're trying to do is become conscious of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.60,0:32:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,cut through the confusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.60,0:32:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,get right to the essential point of that which is effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.60,0:32:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All the dealing with the thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.60,0:32:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all the dealing with the events,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.60,0:32:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all the reasoning and figuring it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.60,0:32:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all the logic,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.60,0:33:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all the probing into the psychological significance and all that is entertaining,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.60,0:33:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's thoroughly ineffective.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.60,0:33:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a waste of time and energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.60,0:33:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It really delays the recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.60,0:33:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The healing of an acute burn of the hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.60,0:33:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,how long does that take?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.60,0:33:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a matter of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.60,0:33:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How long should it take bleeding to stop once you cut off,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.60,0:33:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say, a thumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.60,0:33:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually a matter of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.60,0:33:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Going instantly into this technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.85,0:33:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,for instance when I cut the thumb off,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.85,0:33:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the bleeding led exactly eight drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.85,0:33:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The instant releasing of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.85,0:33:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the releasing of the pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.85,0:33:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the letting go,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.85,0:33:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the resistance of the catastrophic overwhelm,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.85,0:33:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,allowed the thing to stop instantaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.85,0:33:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And those people who tried this technique have had the same experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.33,0:33:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that on the physical level you can demonstrate the truth of what we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.33,0:33:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it with any emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.38,0:33:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You go into the emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.38,0:33:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,then you go past the emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.38,0:33:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you stop calling it anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.38,0:33:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you get in touch with the energy of it that's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.38,0:34:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be coming right up through your solar plexus,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.38,0:34:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or it seems to be everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.38,0:34:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You go right to where experience is being experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.38,0:34:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to use a little discipline with your mind now and refuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.38,0:34:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you can refuse to have your mind fool you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.38,0:34:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The person says,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.46,0:34:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,well I'm experiencing the death of that person out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.46,0:34:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not experiencing it out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.46,0:34:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you're experiencing it in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.46,0:34:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you experiencing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.46,0:34:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're experiencing it in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.46,0:34:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The same place that you always experience experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.46,0:34:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is within your feeling self.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.46,0:34:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your problem is only your own feelingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.46,0:34:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is not the death of someone out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.46,0:34:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the problem is not out there at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.46,0:34:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're up against is the energy of one's own feelingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.46,0:34:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the overwhelm of the energy of the feelingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.46,0:34:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If we direct our attention there and focus it there with precision,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.46,0:34:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that which could be a prolonged and very painful experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.46,0:34:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is aborted,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.46,0:34:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,brought to an abrupt end.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.01,0:35:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens if we keep on letting go of this energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.01,0:35:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens if we welcome it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.01,0:35:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we say,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.01,0:35:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,what an opportunity to decompress all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.01,0:35:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What will be the experience then?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.01,0:35:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be relatively brief,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.11,0:35:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,relatively brief as compared to what it would be
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.11,0:35:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,with an ordinary state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.11,0:35:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happens then is suddenly this energy field stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.11,0:35:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though the decompression chamber,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.11,0:35:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the pressure dial reaches a certain point,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.11,0:35:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and when it reaches that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.46,0:35:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the overflow stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.94,0:35:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then one has a state of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.94,0:35:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.94,0:35:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right out of acute catastrophe come profound states of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.94,0:35:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And those who have been through it know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.98,0:35:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The agony all of a sudden stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.98,0:35:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead there is almost a silence,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.98,0:35:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,an infinite presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.98,0:35:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,an infinite state of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.98,0:35:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that may be greater,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.98,0:35:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,greater than any experience you've had in your life before.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.98,0:36:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When we come out on the other side of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.98,0:36:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.98,0:36:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're lighter,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.98,0:36:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we're freer,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.98,0:36:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we're less subject to pain within our own emotional experience henceforth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.98,0:36:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Clinically,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.67,0:36:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,usually what happens is the person now sighs with relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.67,0:36:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They realize that life is going to go on,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.67,0:36:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that they can live with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.67,0:36:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As bad as it seemed,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.67,0:36:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow one can survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.67,0:36:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And the period of peace goes on for a variable period of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.67,0:36:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there will be a wave of this emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.67,0:36:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and personality coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.67,0:36:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It tends to come back in waves with periods of relief in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.67,0:36:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And what we do is when the wave comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.67,0:36:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,we welcome it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.67,0:36:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We try to release as much out of this valve as we can
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.67,0:36:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,before it shuts off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.96,0:36:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We welcome it as a very valuable opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.96,0:36:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One that may not happen too many times in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.05,0:36:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One to be treasured.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.05,0:36:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The treasuring of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.05,0:36:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the value of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.05,0:36:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,only comes when you're really on the other side of the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.05,0:36:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can look back on it now
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.05,0:36:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,with the wisdom that you've gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.05,0:37:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To say that the mind is not going to really be of any help
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.05,0:37:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in this experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.05,0:37:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the mind is looking in the wrong direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.05,0:37:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is saying to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.05,0:37:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if I could only change the circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.05,0:37:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,or the event out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.05,0:37:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,then I would feel all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.13,0:37:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have some good clinical examples of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.13,0:37:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We've talked in some of these other talks
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.13,0:37:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,about a clinical case I had
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.13,0:37:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of a woman who received a telegram
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.13,0:37:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that her son was killed in Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.13,0:37:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what happened is she stopped talking
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.53,0:37:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and she sat in a rocking chair near the window
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.53,0:37:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and she just kept rocking back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.53,0:37:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and staring numbly out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.53,0:37:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And she was in a state here that we call apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.63,0:37:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Complete loss of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.63,0:37:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The world looked hopeless
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.63,0:37:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and to her, God was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.63,0:37:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She rocked back and forth in this hopeless state
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.80,0:37:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and didn't respond verbally to the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.80,0:37:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Refused to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.80,0:37:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Barely slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.80,0:37:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Took naps perhaps during the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.80,0:38:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But just stared blankly out the window
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.80,0:38:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in a total state of apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.80,0:38:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And we said that certain changes had taken place
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.80,0:38:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in her brain chemistry as a result of this
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.80,0:38:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and the neurotransmitters being depleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.80,0:38:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Some, I think it was about a week or ten days later,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.09,0:38:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the family in the meantime didn't know what to do with this
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.09,0:38:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and was, of course, very disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.09,0:38:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And about a week or ten days later,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.09,0:38:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the family received another telegram from the State Department
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.09,0:38:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,saying that it was all a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.09,0:38:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That the son had not been killed in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.09,0:38:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was another serviceman with the same name
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.09,0:38:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and curiously a number that was only one digit off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.09,0:38:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow there'd been an error in the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.09,0:38:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And so they said to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.15,0:38:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,mother, mother, he's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.15,0:38:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And she went right on rocking,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.15,0:38:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,staring blankly out the window
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.15,0:38:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,as though she didn't even hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.21,0:38:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So changing the circumstances in the outer world
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.21,0:39:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,are not necessarily going to change the upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.21,0:39:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because it has started a process.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.21,0:39:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the process now that has to be handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.21,0:39:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So what has to be accepted at this particular time?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.21,0:39:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the events that have happened out there
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.21,0:39:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's just what you can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.21,0:39:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you can't do is accept the circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.21,0:39:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that have happened in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.21,0:39:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What you can accept
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.21,0:39:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is to surrender to the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.21,0:39:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that you've got to bite the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.21,0:39:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That right now there are times
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.21,0:39:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,when you've got to be with
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.78,0:39:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,your leg is caught in the bear trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.78,0:39:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.78,0:39:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what we surrender to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.78,0:39:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is this experiencing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.78,0:39:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The necessity to sit it through,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.78,0:39:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to face it, to handle with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.78,0:39:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To surrender to the experiencing of the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.78,0:39:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And to use the techniques that we talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.36,0:39:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To be effective then,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.36,0:39:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to pay attention to the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.36,0:39:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the mind really has no solution to this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.36,0:39:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is saying
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.36,0:40:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,if we could only change those external circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.36,0:40:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is where people's experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.36,0:40:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with prayer often come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.36,0:40:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not knowing what to pray for.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.36,0:40:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Later on they may come out of it bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.36,0:40:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they were praying in the wrong direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.36,0:40:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often the prayer goes in the direction of
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.36,0:40:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,please undo that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.36,0:40:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bring joy back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.36,0:40:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bring my thumb back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.36,0:40:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please change what is happening out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.36,0:40:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A prayer in that direction
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.46,0:40:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is very unlikely to be effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.46,0:40:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.46,0:40:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the form of the prayer is like
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.46,0:40:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,dear God please let me be one foot shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.65,0:40:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the problem God's or is the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.65,0:40:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the lack of comprehension of how to pray?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.88,0:40:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point the prayer which says
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.88,0:40:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,please be with me
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.88,0:40:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and show me how to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.88,0:40:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me how to surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.88,0:40:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and how to handle this experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.88,0:40:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The asking for the conscious awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.88,0:40:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.88,0:41:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The asking God to take on the experiencing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.88,0:41:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now curiously enough
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.94,0:41:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,as you keep surrendering into this experience
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.94,0:41:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as you let go resisting it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.86,0:41:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as you let go labeling it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.86,0:41:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you are progressively surrendering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.86,0:41:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,First surrendering that attraction
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.86,0:41:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to pay attention to the thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.86,0:41:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and to do something out there
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.86,0:41:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to try and change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.09,0:41:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the surrendering
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.09,0:41:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to surrendering the labeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.09,0:41:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.67,0:41:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,causing this emotional energy to take form.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.80,0:41:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The surrender to the energy itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.82,0:41:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The total surrender to the energy itself
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.82,0:41:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,brings you into an inner state
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.82,0:41:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,as you keep getting deeper into the surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.82,0:41:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that something is experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.82,0:41:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,something is handling the experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.98,0:41:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of this experience for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.15,0:41:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though the personal self
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.15,0:42:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,now withdraws
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.17,0:42:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the energy is being handled
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.17,0:42:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and what one can say is that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.17,0:42:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy is being handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.11,0:42:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So those who prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.11,0:42:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,those who pray rather
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.11,0:42:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in that direction
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.11,0:42:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to be aware of that which is handling the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.11,0:42:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because as you get deep into the surrender of the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.11,0:42:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you will realize
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.11,0:42:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is being handled for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.11,0:42:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though some energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.11,0:42:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,some infinite mode of existence
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.11,0:42:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,some aspect of beingness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.11,0:42:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is handling it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.11,0:42:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And there comes the surprising realization
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.11,0:42:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that one was never handling it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.11,0:42:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at all to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.11,0:42:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That this was some kind of an illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.11,0:42:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that it was projecting oneself into it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.11,0:42:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,giving it form
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.11,0:42:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,identifying with it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.11,0:42:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that was causing the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.11,0:42:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So the pain is coming from the resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.11,0:42:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the insistence
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.11,0:43:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that the personal self
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.11,0:43:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of its aspects has to handle it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.11,0:43:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that it must do something about the experiences out there
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.11,0:43:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,sue somebody or change the house
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.11,0:43:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,or move to a different location.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.55,0:43:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As it surrenders that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.55,0:43:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and it surrenders its thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.55,0:43:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and it surrenders its wanting to control it and change it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.55,0:43:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and surrenders to the inner experience
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.55,0:43:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and sees that eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.55,0:43:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,as a great gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.55,0:43:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How can it be seen as a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.55,0:43:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Only when we come out the other side of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.38,0:43:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll talk to those who are aligned consciously
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.38,0:43:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in their life with spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.38,0:43:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What does spiritual work look like to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.38,0:43:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You sit back and you ask yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.38,0:43:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,what do I think of is spiritual work?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.38,0:43:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For those of you who don't call it spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.38,0:43:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you might call it consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.38,0:43:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You might call it dealing with your unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.38,0:43:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or your super consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.38,0:43:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you label it, whatever you call it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.38,0:43:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the nature of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.38,0:43:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it look like to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.38,0:44:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've asked three or four people
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.38,0:44:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,who spent many years at it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.38,0:44:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said when you picture spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.03,0:44:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.03,0:44:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And they see a person kneeling down and praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.03,0:44:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They see a person in church.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.03,0:44:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They see a person at a gathering
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.03,0:44:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with everybody holding hands
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.03,0:44:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody saying Aum
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.03,0:44:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and picturing light in the center of the circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.03,0:44:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They picture themselves sitting with a book
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.53,0:44:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and studying late at night
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.53,0:44:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,12, 1 o'clock in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.53,0:44:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They picture themselves listening to audio tapes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.57,0:44:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of well-known spiritual speakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.57,0:44:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They picture themselves at convocations
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.57,0:44:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for body, mind and spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.57,0:44:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and healing services.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.57,0:44:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And so this is a whole panorama of that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.82,0:44:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,which the mind then encompasses
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.82,0:44:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and says that is spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.82,0:44:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But then when faced with a life crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.82,0:44:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it's as though that is excused.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.82,0:44:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.82,0:44:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual work is everybody studying this textbook
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.82,0:44:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and looking at a picture of a guru
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.82,0:45:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and singing songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.82,0:45:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's an acute catastrophe
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.82,0:45:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and we like bypass that now
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.82,0:45:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and we resume our spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.82,0:45:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,after we've sued that son of a bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.82,0:45:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and after we've handled all these various things in our life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.82,0:45:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As a friend of mine once said
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.82,0:45:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,well let's sue them first and then forgive them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.82,0:45:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though one doesn't really see
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.82,0:45:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the essence of spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.82,0:45:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What one doesn't see is that the spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.82,0:45:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,has brought up these acute crises
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.82,0:45:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and brought us into them
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.82,0:45:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and that these are the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.82,0:45:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where the spiritual work is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.82,0:45:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The other was preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.82,0:45:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The other was gathering of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.82,0:45:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The gathering of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.82,0:45:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The deciding on direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.82,0:45:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The accumulating of spiritual knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.17,0:45:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And then comes suddenly the moment of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.21,0:45:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then comes the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.21,0:45:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The time to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.21,0:45:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When we take it out of the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.21,0:46:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we see people who have been in spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.21,0:46:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and around metaphysical circles for years and years
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.21,0:46:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and nothing changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.21,0:46:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.21,0:46:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the same illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.21,0:46:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the same problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.21,0:46:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Their personality is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.21,0:46:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't had any of these experiences of inner truth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.21,0:46:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that they hear about.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.21,0:46:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.21,0:46:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is when life brings to them
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.21,0:46:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the golden opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.21,0:46:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.21,0:46:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time to make that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.21,0:46:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual knowledge real.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.21,0:46:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time for transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.21,0:46:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time to take that leap in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.21,0:46:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These are golden moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.21,0:46:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Acute catastrophes are the times
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.21,0:46:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,when you make great leaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.30,0:46:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When you face it directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.30,0:46:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When you fixedly say,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.30,0:46:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not veer from this spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.30,0:46:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because now what we're really confronted with
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.30,0:46:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is real spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.30,0:46:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not reading some pleasant sounding phrases out of a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.30,0:46:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not looking at the happy picture
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.30,0:46:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of some guru with his robes and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.30,0:46:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're right in the thick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.76,0:46:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're right in the teeth of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.76,0:47:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The teeth of spiritual work is when you're confronted
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.76,0:47:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with that which you cannot avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.76,0:47:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A direct confront that requires a leap in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.76,0:47:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And so these are golden opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.86,0:47:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Priceless.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.86,0:47:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see them as priceless,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.86,0:47:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,your willingness to be with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.86,0:47:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,your willingness to say, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.86,0:47:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your willingness to go with it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.86,0:47:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how painful it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.86,0:47:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then makes a giant leap in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.86,0:47:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A real advance in wisdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.86,0:47:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,knowledge and awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.86,0:47:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you read about within the books
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.86,0:47:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,then becomes your own inner experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.86,0:47:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something below.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.86,0:47:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The emotionality
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.86,0:47:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that is literally experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.17,0:47:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,this energy out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.17,0:47:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's literally being handled
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.17,0:47:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,by something far greater
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.17,0:47:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,than your own personal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.17,0:47:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Were there only the small personal self there,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.17,0:47:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be totally swamped and obliterated
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.17,0:47:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,by the energy released by these experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.17,0:48:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because there is something greater
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.17,0:48:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,than the personal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.17,0:48:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is more than capable of handling it
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.17,0:48:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that allows you to survive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.75,0:48:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The trick of the mind is not to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.75,0:48:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The trick of the mind is to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.75,0:48:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,try to change what goes out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.75,0:48:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.75,0:48:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall back upon the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.75,0:48:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And the intellect is not going to resolve
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.75,0:48:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,this kind of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.75,0:48:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When you've dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.75,0:48:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,a big oak log on your foot
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.75,0:48:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and broken all the bones
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.75,0:48:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,across the front of your foot,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.75,0:48:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what's going to be needed at that moment
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.75,0:48:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is your readiness and your willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.75,0:48:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle that which life presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.75,0:48:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The having the tools,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.75,0:48:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the having the willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.75,0:48:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,brings about a very rapid healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.75,0:48:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There is the awareness and an acute overwhelm
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.75,0:48:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that you really can't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.75,0:48:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,See, part of the panic is the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.75,0:48:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that that which you think you are
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.75,0:48:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,like your own limited self,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.75,0:48:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,relatively powerless,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.75,0:49:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is no match for the power of this experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.90,0:49:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're correct. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.90,0:49:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's precisely what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.90,0:49:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The limited individual personal self
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.90,0:49:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot handle this overwhelm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.90,0:49:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the precise spiritual value of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.94,0:49:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you really want to change
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.94,0:49:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,about the experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.94,0:49:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll see what you want to do
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.94,0:49:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is change how you feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.94,0:49:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how you really feel
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.94,0:49:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,about it and what you can know
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.94,0:49:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the feeling will come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.94,0:49:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The event is not going to bother you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.94,0:49:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,after the feeling state.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.94,0:49:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So all that one has to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.94,0:49:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,through then is the acute upsurge
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.94,0:49:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of this emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.94,0:49:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of this emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.94,0:49:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The events are going to take
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.94,0:49:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,care of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.94,0:49:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire, as you see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.94,0:49:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to change that which occurred out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.94,0:49:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the desire to change
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.94,0:49:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,how you feel about it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.94,0:49:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,has to be surrendered.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.94,0:49:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The confront is there
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.94,0:49:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and all we can do is say yes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.94,0:49:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to experiencing it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.94,0:50:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Death of a loved one, divorce, separation,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.94,0:50:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,acute emergency, catastrophe, injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.94,0:50:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They all bring about
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.94,0:50:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a state of shock
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.94,0:50:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and the shock is the same
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.94,0:50:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what the precipitating event.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.94,0:50:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The shock is the sudden realization
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.94,0:50:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of one's powerlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.94,0:50:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that the will
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.94,0:50:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,has met a brick wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.94,0:50:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The shock that one is stoppable,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.94,0:50:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that one has been stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.94,0:50:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that the personal will
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.94,0:50:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot have its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.94,0:50:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore the shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.94,0:50:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the realization of this
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.94,0:50:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is the same in all the experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.94,0:50:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that it is unchangeable,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.94,0:50:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.94,0:50:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.94,0:50:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though you came up full speed
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.94,0:50:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,against a brick wall
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.94,0:50:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and every time in life
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.94,0:50:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,when we come full speed up against a brick wall
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.94,0:50:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it releases the same energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.94,0:50:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've been through more than one of these experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.94,0:50:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,then look back and you will realize
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.94,0:50:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.94,0:50:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That each time the state of shock was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.94,0:50:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience, the sequence
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.94,0:51:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.94,0:51:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There was the feeling of sudden numbness,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.94,0:51:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the state of disbelief
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.94,0:51:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and then
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.48,0:51:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the unleashing of all the negative feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.48,0:51:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When you look at the negative feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.61,0:51:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,precisely,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.61,0:51:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,when you look back at some of the experiences you have
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.61,0:51:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.61,0:51:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of what we've been saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.61,0:51:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That what you really experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.61,0:51:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.61,0:51:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that not so?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.61,0:51:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You experienced the totality
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.61,0:51:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of that negative energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.61,0:51:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In the morning it would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.61,0:51:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In the afternoon it would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.61,0:51:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, within a minute's time
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.61,0:51:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,we fluctuate back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.61,0:51:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a scintillating energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.61,0:51:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the form of the emotionality
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.67,0:51:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is flickering
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.67,0:51:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,from anger to resentment
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.67,0:51:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to self-pity to jealousy
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.67,0:51:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to getting even to revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.71,0:51:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to hating God, to hating yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.71,0:51:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to hating your family, to blaming society
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.71,0:51:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,blaming the government, blaming the laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.86,0:51:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is wildly racing around
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.86,0:51:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in this negative energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.86,0:52:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I mention this
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.86,0:52:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is I want you to see
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.86,0:52:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the diffuseness of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.86,0:52:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The formlessness of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.86,0:52:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That it is
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.86,0:52:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,like a whole basket of negative
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.86,0:52:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,energy
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.86,0:52:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and we only have to handle the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.86,0:52:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to handle all the little things
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.86,0:52:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that are flickering around in the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.86,0:52:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have to handle
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.86,0:52:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.86,0:52:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if we see that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.00,0:52:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's decompressing the all of it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.00,0:52:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,brings us rapidly through
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.00,0:52:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and out the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.00,0:52:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's an inescapable experience
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.00,0:52:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.00,0:52:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to the work that has to be done now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.00,0:52:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we tell
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.67,0:52:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,when that work is through?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.67,0:52:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we suddenly come out
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.67,0:52:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,into that inner state of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.46,0:52:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We know people, as we said,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.46,0:52:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that years later still have resentments
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.46,0:52:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and are still caught in some aspect
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.46,0:52:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of that negative energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.46,0:52:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it wasn't handled
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.46,0:52:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.88,0:53:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The person has been unwilling to sit down
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.88,0:53:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and handle it until
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.88,0:53:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's through, until it's over,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.88,0:53:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,until it's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.42,0:53:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason, of course, that people
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.42,0:53:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,are unwilling to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.42,0:53:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is because of the pain involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.42,0:53:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they don't know the techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.42,0:53:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because every time they go at it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.42,0:53:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,they start again trying to change
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.42,0:53:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the events in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.42,0:53:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and the thoughts, the intellect
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.42,0:53:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mind trying to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.42,0:53:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They run into the same impasse.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.42,0:53:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So not having an effective tool
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.42,0:53:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with which to handle it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.42,0:53:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the work is left incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.42,0:53:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens with
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.88,0:53:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the incomplete work then?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.88,0:53:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens with the emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.88,0:53:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that were not released?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.19,0:53:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is left undone
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.19,0:53:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to express itself
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.19,0:53:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in emotional attitudes
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.19,0:53:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and begins to express itself
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.19,0:53:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in the body in the form
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.19,0:53:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of emotional illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.19,0:53:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So the unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.19,0:53:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that was not let go of
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.19,0:54:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,over the catastrophe
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.19,0:54:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that happened many years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.19,0:54:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,brings forth through the autonomic
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.19,0:54:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,nervous system and the acupuncture
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.19,0:54:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,energy system and connects up
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.19,0:54:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,with something from mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.19,0:54:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We said mind, the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.19,0:54:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of the intellect, of thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.19,0:54:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is here in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.19,0:54:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of the guilt then
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.19,0:54:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or of the grief, of the fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.19,0:54:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of the anger couples
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.19,0:54:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is some belief system in the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.19,0:54:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,about some particular illness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.19,0:54:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and results then
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.19,0:54:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in a physical illness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.19,0:54:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,which in psychoanalysis
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.19,0:54:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we would say is psychosomatic
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.19,0:54:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in that here the contribution
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.19,0:54:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of the psychological
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.19,0:54:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is on the surface and quite visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.71,0:54:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So the end result
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.71,0:54:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of the unresolved
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.71,0:54:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,handling emotionally
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.71,0:54:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of a catastrophic experience
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.71,0:54:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is often an illness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.71,0:54:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,which may recur many years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.71,0:54:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The grief that was undone
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.71,0:54:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,at the time over the death
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.71,0:54:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of some family member
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.71,0:55:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,20 years later may express itself
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.71,0:55:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,as that heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.26,0:55:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The way we know then
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.94,0:55:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that the thing has been handled
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.94,0:55:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is when we feel at peace about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.94,0:55:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We feel complete about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.94,0:55:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It no longer recurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.94,0:55:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It no longer brings up pain
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.94,0:55:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,when we think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.94,0:55:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We feel satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.94,0:55:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We may regret that we lived through it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.94,0:55:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that we had to live through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.94,0:55:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We came out on the other side of it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.94,0:55:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a different kind of a person
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.94,0:55:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and with that knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.94,0:55:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there comes a certain sense of peace
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.94,0:55:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,telling us that that has been handled now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.94,0:55:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Catastrophic experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.94,0:55:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is the seed, the very essence
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.94,0:55:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of the ultimate
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.94,0:55:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.94,0:55:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Within it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.94,0:55:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and following it to its very center core
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.94,0:55:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and walking off
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.94,0:55:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the cliff totally
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.94,0:55:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the total abandonment
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.94,0:55:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the total surrender to the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.98,0:55:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is the seed,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.98,0:55:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is the very core
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.98,0:56:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which the spiritual seeker
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.98,0:56:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,has been seeking all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.84,0:56:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens in ordinary life
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.84,0:56:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in many catastrophic situations
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.84,0:56:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is an incomplete resolution
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.84,0:56:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.84,0:56:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The not realizing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.84,0:56:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the jewel-like quality
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.84,0:56:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.84,0:56:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the being overwhelmed
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.84,0:56:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,by the what-ness of it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.84,0:56:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,looking in the wrong direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.90,0:56:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of times what happens is
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.90,0:56:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,drugs are introduced
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.90,0:56:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,altered states of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.90,0:56:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so the person is taken to the emergency room
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.90,0:56:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and what could be a crucial
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.90,0:56:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual discovery
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.90,0:56:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,now becomes covered over
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.90,0:56:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so the band-aids over the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.90,0:56:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the family
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.90,0:56:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to distract the person
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.90,0:56:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with watching television
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.90,0:56:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and taking them on trips
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.90,0:56:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the distraction from the spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.90,0:56:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the introduction of things
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.90,0:56:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that alter the state of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.90,0:56:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the person
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.90,0:56:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of running into the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.90,0:57:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,runs away from the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.90,0:57:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The essential aspect
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.09,0:57:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of the spiritual benefit
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.09,0:57:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,comes from running directly
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.09,0:57:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,into the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.09,0:57:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a saying in Zen
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.09,0:57:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to walk straight ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.09,0:57:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.09,0:57:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So when this catastrophic experience
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.09,0:57:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,comes we center ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.09,0:57:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,right into the core of it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.09,0:57:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we say yes to it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.09,0:57:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and we begin to experience it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.96,0:57:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes what happens then
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.96,0:57:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if we refuse to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.09,0:57:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,any band-aids
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.09,0:57:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've had times in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.09,0:57:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,with acute catastrophic experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.09,0:57:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,where there were band-aids available
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.09,0:57:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and I refused them
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.09,0:57:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because by then I had learned the value
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.09,0:57:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of experiencing it through directly
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.17,0:57:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because it really prevents
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.17,0:57:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiencing through
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.17,0:57:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of what we might call hitting bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.17,0:57:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that whole concept of hitting bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.17,0:57:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,which is well known
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.17,0:57:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in handling many serious problems
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.17,0:57:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,such as alcoholism
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.34,0:58:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,which means to let go
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.34,0:58:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and let go completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.34,0:58:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So we see what happens with the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.34,0:58:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is in an acute catastrophic situation
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.34,0:58:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it tries to cling to that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.34,0:58:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,which is familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.34,0:58:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It tries escapism
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.34,0:58:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it tries distractions
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.34,0:58:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it tries tranquilizers and drugs
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.34,0:58:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and alcohol
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.44,0:58:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,various ways of trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.44,0:58:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ameliorate the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.44,0:58:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than facing it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.44,0:58:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and working it through directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.69,0:58:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The essence of a catastrophic situation
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.69,0:58:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is the discovery of that which is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.69,0:58:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is greater than
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.69,0:58:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,one's personal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.73,0:58:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiencing through
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.73,0:58:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,completely of a catastrophe then
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.73,0:58:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,brings one into a connection
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.73,0:58:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is something within oneself
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.73,0:58:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that has the power to sustain
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.73,0:58:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how catastrophic
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.73,0:58:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.73,0:58:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So one comes out on the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.73,0:58:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of it as a greater person
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.73,0:58:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the awareness that there is something within
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.73,0:58:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is a presence
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.73,0:58:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a quality or aspect
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.73,0:59:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of life within oneself
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.73,0:59:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,which has the power
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.73,0:59:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to sustain one through
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.73,0:59:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the most seemingly impossible situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.73,0:59:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.59,0:59:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,catastrophic experience
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.59,0:59:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is not worked through completely
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.59,0:59:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,then we have certain residuals
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.59,0:59:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if you like half fall off the cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.59,0:59:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.59,0:59:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,some people think they've walked off the cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.59,0:59:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but actually we find that they were secretly
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.59,0:59:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,crossing their fingers and hanging on
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.59,0:59:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to some little lifeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.59,0:59:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The abandonment to God was not really total
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.59,0:59:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and so there is left a doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.59,0:59:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of that doubt then
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.59,0:59:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there is the residual
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.59,0:59:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say the residual of grief
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.59,0:59:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the residual of fear of the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.59,0:59:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if there wasn't the experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.59,0:59:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of something greater than the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.59,0:59:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,personal self there
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.59,0:59:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,then we may have an
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.59,0:59:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,end up with a limitation
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.59,0:59:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain crippling
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.59,0:59:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain inability to go
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.59,0:59:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond a certain point
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.59,0:59:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to participate
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.59,1:00:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes limited.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.59,1:00:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I would rather lead a limited life
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.59,1:00:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,than face that kind of experience again
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.59,1:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I would rather never love again
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.59,1:00:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,than to love and lose
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.59,1:00:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the saying is
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.59,1:00:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it is better to have loved and lost
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.59,1:00:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,than never to have loved at all
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.59,1:00:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,because the experience
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.59,1:00:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of loving this
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.59,1:00:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,puts us in touch with our greater self
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.59,1:00:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is greater than our own limited
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.59,1:00:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,small self
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.01,1:00:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the complete resolution then
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.01,1:00:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,brings us into a conscious
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.01,1:00:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,contact with something
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.01,1:00:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,greater than our self
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.01,1:00:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of the hundreds of thousands of people
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.01,1:00:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,who have tried that
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.01,1:00:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and left the record
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.01,1:00:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,they all attest to the fact
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.01,1:00:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that when they surrendered the small self
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.01,1:00:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to something greater than themself
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.01,1:00:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,they came into contact with that
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.01,1:00:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,which they considered to be real
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.01,1:00:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,one's own inner experience
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.01,1:00:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of the spiritual reality
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.01,1:00:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,then takes it from book learning
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.01,1:00:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to a profound inner conviction
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.01,1:00:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,this inner conviction then
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.01,1:01:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.01,1:01:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,comes a willingness
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.01,1:01:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to re-enter into life again
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.01,1:01:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to participate
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.01,1:01:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to take the risk
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.19,1:01:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to take the chances
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.19,1:01:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the inner experience
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.38,1:01:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of getting bottom
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.38,1:01:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's coming out of
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.38,1:01:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,this feeling of hopelessness
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.65,1:01:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and despair
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.65,1:01:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and what is really happening
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.65,1:01:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is the personal small self
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.65,1:01:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is saying
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.65,1:01:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I of my own self
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.65,1:01:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot handle this
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.65,1:01:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it is out of the hopelessness
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.65,1:01:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,then comes the willingness
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.65,1:01:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.65,1:01:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to surrender to something
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.65,1:01:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,greater than oneself
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.34,1:01:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,at the very bottom
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.34,1:01:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in the pits
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.34,1:01:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,one realizes the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.34,1:01:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and accepts the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.34,1:01:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that I of myself
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.34,1:01:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of my own individual
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.34,1:01:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,personal self
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.34,1:01:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,my own ego self
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.34,1:02:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,am unable to handle this
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.34,1:02:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,am unable to resolve it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.34,1:02:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,then the victory
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.34,1:02:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the success arises
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.34,1:02:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the phoenix arises
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.34,1:02:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the ashes
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.34,1:02:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of the despair and hopelessness
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.34,1:02:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't the despair
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.34,1:02:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the hopelessness
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.34,1:02:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that's of the value
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.34,1:02:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the letting go
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.34,1:02:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the realization
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.34,1:02:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of the limitation of the small self
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.34,1:02:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of the catastrophe
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.34,1:02:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the person says
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.34,1:02:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.25,1:02:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the law of free will
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.25,1:02:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and the nature of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.25,1:02:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,being what it is
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.25,1:02:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it is said
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.25,1:02:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that the great beings
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.25,1:02:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that are willing to help all of us
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.25,1:02:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,wait for our saying yes
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.25,1:02:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and so it is the sudden turning then
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.25,1:02:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,from the bottom of the box
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.25,1:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to the willingness
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.25,1:02:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to the acceptance
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.25,1:02:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is something greater than oneself
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.25,1:02:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that one can turn to
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.25,1:02:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and when the person says
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.25,1:03:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.25,1:03:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,one can turn to
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.25,1:03:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and he becomes not just a free will
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.25,1:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but a person is
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.25,1:03:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,he has already turned
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.25,1:03:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,from the beginning
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.25,1:03:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,into the nature of the purpose
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.25,1:03:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of the purpose
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.25,1:03:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of the purpose
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.25,1:03:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and he is now
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.25,1:03:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,given a new form
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.25,1:03:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a new form of faith
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.25,1:03:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a new form of healing
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.40,1:03:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and he gains
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.40,1:03:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a new form of life
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.40,1:03:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,moment came a great transformative experience, the spiritual power of which is evident from
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.96,1:03:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the millions of lives that have been affected by the energy that flowed out into the world
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.19,1:03:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,by this man sharing his spiritual experience. So letting go and hitting bottom then are
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.88,1:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,crucial. It is out of the awareness that one cannot change it, that one is limited, that
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.38,1:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,one is powerless. So the powerlessness then is the very source of the discovery of that
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.63,1:04:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,which does have the power in the universe. That power comes in and handles the experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.03,1:04:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We know when that happens because of the profound state of peace. Where there was agony, now
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.96,1:04:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a state of infinite peace and the ineffable awareness of an infinite presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.96,1:04:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Historically,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.23,1:04:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it has been a special case out of which a realization of the truth has arisen, but it
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.36,1:04:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is not at all necessary. It is only one type of experience. Actually, spiritual work is
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.26,1:04:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of this nature all the time. The person who is involved in spiritual work is always looking
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.46,1:04:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,at what is coming up in life, seeing what is coming up in life as the teacher, the grist
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.86,1:04:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for the millstone.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.23,1:05:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is what is happening that represents that which is being worked on. So an acute catastrophe
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.82,1:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,then would just be a continuation of the process that is going on anyway. So the person
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.96,1:05:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,who is intensely involved in spiritual work, then it would be seen as a golden opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.59,1:05:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,painful and regretful perhaps, and yet one of great benefit. So the essential nature
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.84,1:05:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of spiritual work is remaining the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.78,1:05:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To remain focused on that which is rising from instant to instant, always looking at
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.59,1:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,experiencing, what is experiencing, where is it being experienced, what is experiencing
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.75,1:05:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.23,1:05:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a meditative technique then which is one that is used. The same result comes
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.01,1:05:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,about.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.92,1:05:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The constantly letting go, wanting to control. The experiencing the quality of experiencing
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.90,1:05:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.82,1:05:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,cham
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.11,1:05:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the sudden coming into the state of attainment.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.73,1:05:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,colon
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.82,1:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience that it is being handled by some infinite aspect of oneself, hitherto
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.82,1:06:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,fore suspected perhaps, but not actually realized. The realization of the presence after that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.00,1:06:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes more and more frequent.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.36,1:06:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of this experience then comes an ever-grating willingness to rely on that inner presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.78,1:06:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Less and less of a reliance on the smaller self. Less and less does the person look to
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.88,1:06:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,this small self to handle life's problems. There's a progressive willingness to surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.19,1:06:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to one's higher self, the progressive loss of identification, and the increasing identification
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.73,1:06:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,with that presence. The willingness then to surrender life in all of its aspects to the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.94,1:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,will of God becomes the very present.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.76,1:07:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The acute catastrophic experience then is a key learning experience, a key learning
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.51,1:07:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,experience in that we learn to go to the very core, to the very essence of the experience
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.17,1:07:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to see what it is and handle it right at the level of experiencing, right within the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.92,1:07:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,field of consciousness itself. The willingness to surrender, to let go, wanting to change
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.53,1:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened out there. The letting go of wanting to change the thinking about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.96,1:07:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to handle it with the intellect. The letting go of trying to handle it with the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.88,1:07:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,emotions. The willingness to surrender to the essence of the experience without calling
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.57,1:07:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it anything, without labeling it, without putting names on it. The willingness to handle
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.75,1:07:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field of it, to go directly to the inner experience. And the surrender to
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.61,1:07:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the inner experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.53,1:07:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And is the open doorway to the experience of something greater than the small personal
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.01,1:08:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,self.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.46,1:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Each catastrophe then is a repeat, the re-presentation of another opportunity for this great spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.42,1:08:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,learning experience. And therefore we hear people who have been through great catastrophic
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.28,1:08:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences express their gratitude. We will hear people say, although I wouldn't want
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.36,1:08:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to live through it again, I'm very grateful for that experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.97,1:08:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We refer back to Alcoholics Anonymous again, we will hear people say that they're grateful
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.39,1:08:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're an alcoholic. How could a person be grateful for that which the world considers
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.56,1:08:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a terrible catastrophe, and a terrible progressive illness? It's because what they learn out
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.60,1:08:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of this catastrophe was of such a great dimension that the price was worth it. So if we handle
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.27,1:08:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,this experience correctly, we will later look back on it and will say that the price was
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.78,1:08:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,worth it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.78,1:08:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for Dr. Dain Heer's Remote View of Transition and True Consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.78,1:08:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Dain Heer's Remote View of Transition and True Consciousness. NTW.com.au.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.97,1:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the reconnection with the essential core of our beingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.86,1:09:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the realization of truth, made whatever the price was worth, worth it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.44,1:09:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As we grow spiritually and as we become spiritually educated,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.06,1:09:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it takes less and less to bring about the willingness to face this inner experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.89,1:09:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We might say that a person's bottom gets progressively raised.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.60,1:09:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A person doesn't have to go through agonizing pain
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.40,1:09:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,before they are willing to let go and surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.63,1:09:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more, there arises the willingness to do it on a daily basis
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.75,1:09:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so that it becomes part and parcel of one's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.97,1:09:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The constant looking at how I'm trying to control things,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.52,1:09:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,how I'm trying to change God's will about how I'm going to try and change God and control God.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.81,1:09:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to totally surrender at great depth.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.35,1:09:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we see surrender occurs at different depths.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.47,1:09:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In ordinary life,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.40,1:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we surrender a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.40,1:09:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Under greater pressure, we're willing to surrender more.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.40,1:10:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We realize that we don't have to put ourself under catastrophic pressure
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.40,1:10:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to be willing to surrender at great depth.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.40,1:10:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The transformation of personality,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.18,1:10:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole shift in one's spiritual position,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.18,1:10:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,traditionally comes from surrendering at great depth.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.18,1:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we become interested in what does that mean, surrendering at great depth.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.18,1:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we surrender at great depth?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.18,1:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we surrender at great depth?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.18,1:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Without having to put ourself through a terrible emotional catastrophe
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.18,1:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to accomplish the same spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.18,1:10:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,By seeing the essential nature of the process, then,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.23,1:10:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we become educated.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.23,1:10:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Our position shifts and we are different in the way that we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.23,1:10:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're willing to be with life in all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.23,1:10:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That willingness, then, is experienced as an inner state of aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.23,1:10:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming out of that willingness to take the chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.23,1:10:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we now know that we are accompanied by something greater than that personal self.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.39,1:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't the personal self that has to handle what comes up in life.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.39,1:11:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That there is always with us that infinite presence,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.39,1:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,more powerful than the human will and ego.
